snippet.title: IDIOTIC (The Game) - Trailer 3
snippet.description:
Phew, it's been a while since the first two (rushed) trailers. Now there's more to the game than what showed in the trailer, amazing! right?

Thanks again to everyone who followed the development! This game really wouldn't have been made without your support!

The game will release on March 3rd. You can find it on Steam here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1746520/IDIOTIC_The_Game/
